OL,6,FReporter Katie Cole was at Newcastle
OL,7,FCrown Court for the sentencing of Ben
OL,8,FHughes
OL,10,FA man has been sentenced to life in
OL,11,Fprison with a minimum of 17 and a half
OL,12,Fyears for the murder of a woman in
OL,13,FGateshead.
OL,15,F39-year-old Ben Hughes admitted to
OL,16,Fkilling 37-year-old Laura Robson, was
OL,17,Fstabbed 27 times during an attack at a
OL,18,Fhouse in Appledore Close Greenside in
OL,19,FJuly 2024.
