OL,6,FHughes pleaded guilty to her murder at
OL,7,Fa court hearing in November 2024 and
OL,8,Fhad been remanded in custody until
OL,9,Ftoday's sentencing.
OL,11,FThe court heard how the mother-of-
OL,12,Fthree had come to Hughes' flat in
OL,13,FGreenside near Ryton on 22 July 2024.
OL,14,FThe pair had known each other for just
OL,15,Fa few days after meeting through a
OL,16,Ffriend.
OL,18,FThe court was also told how that same
OL,19,Fnight, Laura had sent a text to a
OL,20,Ffriend to say things were not good and
OL,21,Fthat she was returning home.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/8
