OL,6,FHowever, a few minutes later a
OL,7,Fneighbour of Hughes called the police
OL,8,Fto report hearing loud screams and
OL,9,Fcries help coming from Hughes' flat.
OL,11,FThe neighbour heard Laura calling out
OL,12,Fthat she was about to die going to die
OL,13,Fand was going to "bleed out", with
OL,14,FHughes replying that she was going to
OL,15,Fdie anyway and that nobody was coming
OL,16,Fto help her.
OL,18,FLaura's body was found in the front
OL,19,Froom of the house by Emergency
OL,20,Fservices. She was declared her dead at
OL,21,Fthe scene.
