OL,6,FHughes appeared for sentencing via
OL,7,Fvideo link, but walked out of
OL,8,Fproceedings after becoming disruptive.
OL,9,FIn his absence, he was handed a life
OL,10,Fsentence and will serve a minimum of
OL,11,F17 and a half years in prison.
OL,13,FIn an emotional statement read to the
OL,14,Fcourt, Laura's mother Jill Evans said:
OL,15,F"The hardest part for me is knowing
OL,16,Fshe won't walk back through the door.
OL,17,FIt is constantly in my mind, that
OL,18,Fnight.
