OL,6,F"They have been put through a
OL,7,Fhorrendous ordeal and hope they can
OL,8,Ftake a degree of closure now Laura's
OL,9,Fkiller has been jailed.
OL,11,F"Ben Hughes is an extremely dangerous
OL,12,Findividual who has taken the life of a
OL,13,Fcompletely innocent woman.
OL,15,F"Through our investigation we found
OL,16,Fthat he had only known Laura for a
OL,17,Fmatter of days before he subjected her
OL,18,Fto a violent assault which claimed her
OL,19,Flife.
